Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lôi Minh Trảm!{cú chém bằng sấm?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fscx100\fscy100\c&HDFE3E6&\bord0\blur3\bord5\\b1\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs100\pos(980,358)}Cú\NChém\NSấm\NSét
